<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>PyroHawk — Wildfire Prevention Drone</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;700&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --fire: #FF4500;
    --ember: #FF8C00;
    --bg: #141414;
    --card: #1e1e1e;
    --border: #2e2e2e;
    --text: #e8e4dc;
    --muted: #888;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    padding: 1.25rem 6vw;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background: rgba(20,20,20,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    z-index: 100;
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .nav-logo span { color: var(--fire); }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--fire); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 10rem 6vw 6rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; right: 0;
    width: 50%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 40%, rgba(255,69,0,0.1) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fire);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,69,0,0.3);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: up 0.7s 0.1s forwards;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(4.5rem, 12vw, 10rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: up 0.7s 0.3s forwards;
  }

  h1 span { color: var(--fire); }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.5vw, 1.1rem);
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 480px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: up 0.7s 0.5s forwards;
  }

  .stats-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: up 0.7s 0.7s forwards;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .stat {
    padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }

  .stat-n {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: var(--fire);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-l {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }

  /* DRONE PHOTO */
  .photo-section {
    padding: 5rem 6vw;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .photo-wrap {
    position: relative;
  }

  .photo-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 3px;
    display: block;
    filter: contrast(1.05) saturate(0.85);
  }

  .photo-label {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    background: rgba(20,20,20,0.85);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .photo-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .photo-text h2 span { color: var(--fire); }

  .photo-text p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* SECTION HEADER */
  .section-head {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fire);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-head h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .section-head h2 span { color: var(--fire); }

  /* HOW IT WORKS */
  .how-section {
    padding: 5rem 6vw;
    background: var(--card);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .how-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .how-card {
    background: var(--card);
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: background 0.25s;
  }

  .how-card:hover { background: #242424; }

  .how-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: rgba(255,69,0,0.18);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .how-title {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .how-body {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* DROPPER */
  .dropper-section {
    padding: 5rem 6vw;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .dropper-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .dropper-diagram {
    position: sticky;
    top: 5rem;
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .dropper-diagram svg { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }

  .diagram-caption {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  .step {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .step:first-child { padding-top: 0; }

  .step-n {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--border);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 1.8rem;
    transition: color 0.25s;
  }

  .step:hover .step-n { color: var(--fire); }

  .step-title {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }

  .step-body {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* COST */
  .cost-section {
    padding: 5rem 6vw;
    background: var(--card);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .cost-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .cost-card {
    background: var(--card);
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .cost-card.hl {
    background: rgba(255,69,0,0.05);
    position: relative;
  }

  .cost-card.hl::after {
    content: 'PyroHawk';
    position: absolute;
    top: 1rem; right: 1rem;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--fire);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .cost-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .cost-price {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .cost-price span { color: var(--fire); }

  .cost-unit {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cost-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.45rem;
  }

  .cost-list li {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cost-list li::before {
    content: '–';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--fire);
  }

  /* BOM TABLE */
  .bom-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fire);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  th {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: left;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  td {
    padding: 0.65rem 0.75rem;
    color: #999;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
  }

  tr:hover td { color: var(--text); background: rgba(255,69,0,0.02); }
  td:first-child { color: var(--text); font-weight: 400; }

  /* ROADMAP */
  .roadmap-section {
    padding: 5rem 6vw;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .tracks {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .track-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fire);
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .milestone {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .m-n {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--border);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: color 0.25s;
  }

  .milestone:hover .m-n { color: var(--fire); }

  .m-title {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }

  .m-body {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    padding: 2.5rem 6vw;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .foot-logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .foot-logo span { color: var(--fire); }

  .foot-note {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* REVEAL */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(16px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  .reveal.on { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  @keyframes up {
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .photo-section, .dropper-layout, .tracks { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .how-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cost-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .dropper-diagram { position: static; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .stats-row { flex-direction: column; width: 100%; }
    .stat { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">PYRO<span>HAWK</span></div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#how">How It Works</a></li>
    <li><a href="#dropper">Mechanism</a></li>
    <li><a href="#cost">Cost</a></li>
    <li><a href="#roadmap">Roadmap</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="tag">Cooper Summer STEM &nbsp;·&nbsp; Wildfire Prevention</div>
  <h1>PYRO<span>HAWK</span></h1>
  <p class="hero-desc">An autonomous drone system for precision prescribed burning. PyroHawk drops ignited fire pellets at GPS-targeted locations, allowing fire management teams to conduct controlled burns safely and without entering hazardous terrain.</p>
  <div class="stats-row">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-n">+14K</div>
      <div class="stat-l">More wildfires 2024→2025</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-n">−16%</div>
      <div class="stat-l">Burn severity reduction</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-n">−14%</div>
      <div class="stat-l">Emissions reduction</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PHOTO -->
<section class="photo-section reveal">
  <div class="photo-wrap">
    <img src="1772994049009_image.png" alt="Heavy-lift drone with pellet dispenser payload — PyroHawk reference concept" />
    <div class="photo-label">Reference concept — heavy-lift drone with pellet dispenser payload</div>
  </div>
  <div class="photo-text">
    <h2>Built for <span>Rough Terrain</span></h2>
    <p>Traditional prescribed burning requires ground crews to travel through dangerous backcountry terrain, making the process slow, expensive, and risky. PyroHawk removes people from the equation entirely.</p>
    <p>Mounted beneath a heavy-lift drone frame, the custom pellet dispenser stores fire pellets in a conical hopper, dispenses them one at a time through a servo-controlled gate, ignites each one on-board using a nichrome wire system, and drops them with precision at designated coordinates.</p>
    <p>The result is controlled burns executed autonomously, at scale, with no crew in the burn zone.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="how-section" id="how">
  <div class="section-head reveal">
    <div class="section-tag">System Overview</div>
    <h2>How It <span>Works</span></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="how-grid reveal">
    <div class="how-card">
      <div class="how-num">01</div>
      <div class="how-title">Airframe</div>
      <div class="how-body">Echo 5" frame with four Readytosky RS2205 brushless motors and HQProp 3-blade propellers. SpeedyBee V5 flight stack sits on vibration-damping pads at center. GPS module feeds positioning data to the flight controller in real time.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="how-card">
      <div class="how-num">02</div>
      <div class="how-title">Pellet Dropper</div>
      <div class="how-body">A conical hopper feeds pellets one at a time through a servo-gated exit. Each pellet passes down a ceramic drop tube, is clamped, ignited by a nichrome wire system, then released at the GPS target. All drop-path components are fire-resistant.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="how-card">
      <div class="how-num">03</div>
      <div class="how-title">AI Navigation</div>
      <div class="how-body">Swin-UNet (a Vision Transformer) maps the terrain from live camera feed. A modified TrailNet model processes that map and outputs target GPS coordinates. ArduPilot executes the flight via MAVLink protocol in Guided Flight Mode, fully autonomously.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="how-card">
      <div class="how-num">04</div>
      <div class="how-title">Onboard Compute</div>
      <div class="how-body">A Jetson Orin-Nano handles the full AI pipeline in real time — running terrain segmentation, navigation inference, and flight control communication simultaneously. The entire system loops continuously with no human input required mid-mission.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="how-card">
      <div class="how-num">05</div>
      <div class="how-title">Ignition Safety</div>
      <div class="how-body">Arduino ESP32 controls a multi-relay nichrome ignition system, keeping each burn short and repeatable. Ignition is tested entirely separately from the drone in a controlled environment. No ignition testing is performed during flight tests.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="how-card">
      <div class="how-num">06</div>
      <div class="how-title">CAD Design</div>
      <div class="how-body">The full mechanical layout — hopper, release gate, servo mount, camera positions, and wiring paths — is designed in Fusion 360 before any parts are built. PA6-CF filament is used for fire-resistant 3D-printed components, produced on school equipment.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DROPPER MECHANISM -->
<section class="dropper-section" id="dropper">
  <div class="section-head reveal">
    <div class="section-tag">Payload Detail</div>
    <h2>Pellet Drop <span>Mechanism</span></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="dropper-layout reveal">
    <div class="dropper-diagram">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 200 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <!-- Hopper -->
        <polygon points="20,10 180,10 155,95 45,95" fill="#242424" stroke="#3a3a3a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <!-- Pellets -->
        <circle cx="80" cy="40" r="9" fill="#FF4500" opacity="0.75"/>
        <circle cx="100" cy="35" r="9" fill="#FF5520" opacity="0.75"/>
        <circle cx="120" cy="40" r="9" fill="#FF4500" opacity="0.75"/>
        <circle cx="90" cy="55" r="9" fill="#FF4A10" opacity="0.75"/>
        <circle cx="112" cy="54" r="9" fill="#FF4500" opacity="0.75"/>
        <text x="100" y="88" text-anchor="middle" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="7" fill="#555" letter-spacing="1">HOPPER</text>
        <!-- Servo block -->
        <rect x="45" y="95" width="110" height="45" fill="#1e1e1e" stroke="#3a3a3a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <rect x="60" y="103" width="35" height="28" rx="2" fill="#141414" stroke="#FF4500" stroke-width="1"/>
        <line x1="95" y1="117" x2="120" y2="126" stroke="#FF4500" stroke-width="2"/>
        <circle cx="120" cy="126" r="3" fill="#FF4500"/>
        <text x="100" y="130" text-anchor="middle" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="7" fill="#555" letter-spacing="1">SERVO GATE</text>
        <!-- Tube -->
        <rect x="82" y="140" width="36" height="100" rx="1" fill="#181818" stroke="#3a3a3a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <text x="140" y="193" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="7" fill="#555" letter-spacing="1">CERAMIC</text>
        <text x="140" y="203" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="7" fill="#555" letter-spacing="1">TUBE</text>
        <!-- Pellet in tube -->
        <circle cx="100" cy="185" r="11" fill="#FF4500" opacity="0.8"/>
        <!-- Ignition wire -->
        <path d="M68 215 Q100 208 132 215" stroke="#FF8C00" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="3,2"/>
        <text x="30" y="220" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="6.5" fill="#FF8C00" letter-spacing="1">IGNITION</text>
        <!-- Clamp -->
        <rect x="78" y="240" width="44" height="26" rx="2" fill="#1e1e1e" stroke="#3a3a3a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <line x1="78" y1="253" x2="65" y2="253" stroke="#444" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="122" y1="253" x2="135" y2="253" stroke="#444" stroke-width="2"/>
        <text x="100" y="257" text-anchor="middle" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="6.5" fill="#555" letter-spacing="1">CLAMP</text>
        <!-- Arrow + dropping pellet -->
        <line x1="100" y1="268" x2="100" y2="295" stroke="#FF4500" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4,3"/>
        <polygon points="95,292 105,292 100,302" fill="#FF4500"/>
        <circle cx="100" cy="325" r="11" fill="#FF4500" opacity="0.5"/>
        <circle cx="100" cy="355" r="9" fill="#FF4500" opacity="0.25"/>
        <circle cx="100" cy="382" r="7" fill="#FF4500" opacity="0.1"/>
        <text x="118" y="329" font-family="IBM Plex Mono" font-size="7" fill="#FF4500" letter-spacing="1">DROP</text>
      </svg>
      <div class="diagram-caption">Pellet flow — side cross section</div>
    </div>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-n">1</div>
        <div>
          <div class="step-title">Hopper Storage</div>
          <div class="step-body">Wood pellets are loaded into the conical hopper, which funnels them by gravity toward a single-pellet exit hole at the base. The geometry ensures a consistent single-file flow.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-n">2</div>
        <div>
          <div class="step-title">Servo Gate</div>
          <div class="step-body">An MG996R servo rotates a short lever to push exactly one pellet into the drop tube, then immediately resets to block the next one. This gives precise per-pellet control and prevents double-drops.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-n">3</div>
        <div>
          <div class="step-title">Ceramic Drop Tube</div>
          <div class="step-body">The pellet travels down a slim, fire-resistant ceramic tube into a holding clamp below. The tube is aligned vertically to ensure a consistent drop trajectory regardless of drone orientation.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-n">4</div>
        <div>
          <div class="step-title">Nichrome Ignition</div>
          <div class="step-body">While clamped, an Arduino ESP32-controlled relay activates nichrome wire around the pellet for a short, programmable duration. The relay then cuts power before release, protecting the mechanism from heat damage.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-n">5</div>
        <div>
          <div class="step-title">Precision Drop</div>
          <div class="step-body">The clamp releases the ignited pellet at the GPS-designated target. ArduPilot logs the drop location and immediately re-runs the AI navigation model to select the next drop point.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

